  titleVerse: 
  passionText: 'Vengeance: Restore SPI when achieving a worthy revenge.

    In serenous
    moon the best of us can rest in docile light

    The quietest bird in impure
    times must soar in grisly flight

    Dove Knight

    WINGED ARMOUR

    Ability
    Limitation

    1 Always land safely Sink like a stone

    2 Jump twice as high
    Red glow when angry

    3 Sprint silently Slow running speed

    4 Animals
    won''t attack

    you unprovoked

    Horses other than your

    own are afraid
    of you

    5

    Knights who strike the

    first blow against you

    lose
    d6 SPI

    Lose d6 SPI if you ever

    strike the first blow to

    a Knight

    6
    Appear as real wings Only protects under

    daylight'
